## Limitations
The findings in this report are based on available online resources and may not encompass all aspects of domestic violence's societal impact. Some sources may lack recent data or comprehensive analysis, and the scope of the report is limited to the information accessible through the selected sources. Further research, including empirical studies and data from diverse geographical regions, would provide a more comprehensive understanding of the issue.